name: Pin Up Players Playing Cards
description: Taking note from the pin up illustrators of yesterday, photographer/artist Adam Ramirez puts a modern twist on nostalgia and novelty with this brand new deck of playing cards. Pin Up Players features 5 of today's up-and-coming models leaving their own sultry signature for each suit including: ♥ Crystal Lynn ♣ zaR! ♦ Miss Bea Rock ♠ Miss Mary Leigh • Kat Gun These 2.5" x 3.5" playing cards come in a protective case with 54 individual custom designs. Come get 'em while they’re HOT! Ships in 2-4 Weeks.

name: Pin Up Originals: Miss Bea Rock
description: In this latest series of limited edition prints, Pin Up Originals, photographer Adam Ramirez utilizes the initial photographs used to create Pin Up Players. This modern throwback to vintage photography is printed on the finest archival paper assuring preservation through those golden years. Each print comes with a Certificate of Authenticity & Bio card for each corresponding model. "Pin Up Originals: Miss Bea Rock" Size: 8" x 12" Signed and Numbered Edition of 20. Comes with Signed and Numbered COA. Includes Limited Edition Bio Card $20 + shipping Ships in 2-4 Weeks.
